{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrastertilesource\/initwithidentifier:configurationurl:"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"instancetype"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithIdentifier:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"configurationURL:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL","text":"NSURL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"configurationURL","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"identifier","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A string that uniquely identifies the source in the style to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which it is added."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"configurationURL","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A URL to a TileJSON configuration file describing the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source’s contents and other metadata."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","text":"Return Value","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An initialized raster tile source.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After initializing and configuring the source, add it to a map view’s style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"using the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/addSource:","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The URL may be a full HTTP or HTTPS URL or canonical URL. The URL should"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"point to a JSON file that conforms to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TileJSON specification"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If a Mapbox URL is specified, this source uses a tile size of 256. For all"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other tilesets, the default value is 512. (See the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize"},{"type":"text","text":" documentation for more information about tile"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sizes.) If you need to use a tile size other than the default, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:tileSize:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a raster tile source initialized with an identifier and configuration"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"URL."}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNRasterTileSource(im)initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","kind":"identifier"}]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource\/initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNRasterTileSource/initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource\/initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a raster tile source initialized with an identifier and configuration"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"URL."}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrastertilesource\/initwithidentifier:configurationurl:","title":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNRasterTileSource":{"title":"MLNRasterTileSource","fragments":[{"text":"MLNRasterTileSource","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource"},{"text":" is a map content source that supplies raster image tiles","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to be shown on the map. The location of and metadata about the tiles are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"defined either by an option dictionary or by an external file that conforms to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TileJSON specification","type":"text"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A raster tile source is added to an ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},{"text":" object along with one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterStyleLayer"},{"text":" objects. Use a raster style layer to control the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"appearance of content supplied by the raster tile source.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrastertilesource","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource","role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize":{"abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSNumber","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" object containing a floating-point number that specifies the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"width and height (measured in points) at which the map displays each raster","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"image tile when the map’s zoom level is an integer. The raster tile source","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"scales its images up or down when the map’s zoom level falls between two","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"integers.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize","title":"MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntilesourceoptiontilesize"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNStyle":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The proxy object for the current map style.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnstyle","title":"MLNStyle","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNStyle"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNRasterStyleLayer":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNRasterStyleLayer","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrasterstylelayer","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterStyleLayer"},{"type":"text","text":" is a style layer that renders georeferenced raster"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"imagery on the map, especially raster tiles."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterStyleLayer","fragments":[{"text":"MLNRasterStyleLayer","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNStyle/addSource:":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnstyle\/addsource:","title":"addSource:","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"addSource:"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Adds a new source to the current style.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/addSource:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addSource:"}]}}}